Operators:operator are symbols or concepts to perform business logic or operation 
1.Arithmetic 
+,-,*,/,%,++,--
2.Relational:
>,<,>=,<=,==,!=
3.Logical:
&&->AND,->it will only be true if both the condition are true else false.
||->OR->if both are false otherwise it will 
!-NOT->
4.Assignment=>
=,+=,-=,*=,/=,%= 
5.Bitwise-we perform an operation on bit
10=>convert them to binary =bitwise operation=>Decimal
6.Ternary:
?:

7.preincrement and decrement
++
--
